measurements.description: Nine flowers and two buds on one 96-cm inflorescence; sepals white overlaid light green, burgundy spots and stripes, burgundy blush marginally; petals white, overlaid light green, burgundy stripes, blushed burgundy marginally; lip margin ruffled, white, blotched burgundy along edges, central burgundy stripe; column white, blushed burgundy, burgundy stripes ventrally, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
